body:
{CoreyMcCormack}
That’s easy, Joey. It was the first week back after the trip. I sent Carey a Snapchat and he didn’t even open it. When I asked him
if he’d seen it, he said, “What’s a Snapchat?” and then started talking about how he can’t keep up with all these new words and 
the rent is too high.
